Output assets/quick_start_3.gif
Require dart
Set Margin 0
Set BorderRadius 0
Set WindowBar ""
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 950
Set Height 180
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "OneDark"

Hide
Type "clear && dart run example/quick_start_3.dart"
Enter
Show

Sleep 1s
Type "supersecret"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 1s
Right 4
Sleep 500ms
Left 2
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 2s
